<paragraph id="B48181CD60EEC1ABC1DD6B07A3539CBE" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">
<emphasis id="5DCFDF153335FE1ABB6DAE9F3EBA1BFD" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Italy. Emilia-Romagna.</emphasis>
Ventasso (Reggio Emilia), Monte Prado (WGS84 44.252477N, 
<geoCoordinate id="1F310ABE0F8AA3E99E9D55A86AB40A87" degrees="10.400372" direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="1" value="10.400372">10.400372E</geoCoordinate>
